# Tauri app icons are generated, not committed by hand.
# Before your first build, generate them from a 1024×1024 PNG:
#
#   npm run tauri icon path/to/helm-1024.png
#
# This populates 32x32.png, 128x128.png, 128x128@2x.png, icon.icns, and
# icon.ico here — the files referenced by bundle.icon in tauri.conf.json.
